DESCRIPTION:A short planning call for Section Leaders and Assistants across the Brussels District ahead of the autumn term. We&amp\;rsquo\;ll cover the term card\, the District camp shortlist\, safeguarding refresher dates\, and any help needed on the volunteer rota.\nDial-in details will be sent by email the day before. If you can&amp\;rsquo\;t make it\, drop the GSL a note and we&amp\;rsquo\;ll fold your input into the notes.\n
